{
  "stem": "11089.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name is Irving, I-R-V-I-N-G, Eisner, E-I-S-N-E-R.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My birth date is March the 10th, 1926.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born in a small village called [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sojmo, ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "S-O-J-M-O, ?] in Czechoslovakia, in the Carpathian Hills.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before we go on to talk about your pre-war life in Sojmy, I wanted to ask you, was the name Irving Eisner the name that you were born with?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was born with a Hebrew name, Yitzhak.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as our part of this particular part of the world was changed, the names was also changed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I recall I was once called Ignatz, I-G-N-A-T-Z, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and Yitzhak, and today, Irving.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember more names.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We'd like to learn from you about your family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Tell me about your father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What was his name?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father's name was Joseph, J-O-S-E-P-H, Joseph Eisner.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a child, one boy of-- and five sisters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He lost his parents, he told me, very young.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, I only remember a little bit of one of my grandparents, his father, called Nahum.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was nine when he lost his father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was 11 when he lost his mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And because to keep up some supporting, his sisters, he went to work in stores all over, what he could.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he succeeded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all his life he was only in business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "From the very beginning till the very end, his major business was lumber.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had our own forests and he became very famous.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And considering that time, he was also very rich in the lumber.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was succeeding to marry out his five sisters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And to each sister, he build a house out of wood.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was so successful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was an Orthodox man, modern.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Didn't have a beard.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
